# Subscription Model — Education Management System

## Architecture

```
Organization (billing entity — owns subscription)
├── Institution A  (school)
├── Institution B  (college)
└── Institution C  (coaching)
```

- **Subscription lives on `organizations`** table
- Each plan includes N institutions; extras via add-on
- Users/storage/emails are counted org-wide across all institutions

---

## Pricing Tiers (all ₹ INR)

| | **Starter** | **Professional** | **Enterprise** | **Plus** |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Monthly** | ₹1,499 | ₹3,999 | ₹7,999 | ₹14,999 |
| **Annual** (per mo) | ₹1,249 | ₹3,332 | ₹6,666 | ₹12,499 |
| Institutions | **1** | **3** | **10** | **Unlimited** |
| Users (total) | 200 | 1,000 | 5,000 | Unlimited |
| Staff accounts | 5 | 20 | Unlimited | Unlimited |
| Emails/month | 1,000 | 5,000 | 20,000 | Unlimited |
| Storage | 2 GB | 10 GB | 50 GB | 200 GB |

