## Add-Ons (any tier)

| Add-On | Price |
|---|---|
| Extra Institution | ₹999/mo each |
| SMS Notifications | ₹499/mo + ₹0.25/SMS |
| Payment Gateway (Razorpay) | ₹999/mo + 2% per txn |
| Extra Storage (10 GB) | ₹199/mo |
| Extra Users (100) | ₹299/mo |
| Extra Emails (1,000) | ₹99/mo |
| Custom Domain SSL | ₹499/mo |

