## Profit Analysis

| Tier | Price | Infra Cost | Margin |
|---|---|---|---|
| Starter (1 inst) | ₹1,499 | ₹880 | **41%** |
| Pro (3 inst) | ₹3,999 | ₹1,200 | **70%** |
| Enterprise (10 inst) | ₹7,999 | ₹2,500 | **69%** |
| Plus (unlimited) | ₹14,999 | ₹5,000 | **67%** |

All tiers well above the required 2% minimum.

