## Database Schema

Subscription columns go on `organizations` table:

```sql
ALTER TABLE organizations ADD COLUMN subscription_tier VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'starter';
ALTER TABLE organizations ADD COLUMN max_institutions INTEGER DEFAULT 1;
ALTER TABLE organizations ADD COLUMN max_users INTEGER DEFAULT 200;
ALTER TABLE organizations ADD COLUMN max_staff INTEGER DEFAULT 5;
ALTER TABLE organizations ADD COLUMN max_emails_per_month INTEGER DEFAULT 1000;
ALTER TABLE organizations ADD COLUMN storage_quota_gb INTEGER DEFAULT 2;
ALTER TABLE organizations ADD COLUMN billing_cycle VARCHAR(10) DEFAULT 'monthly';
ALTER TABLE organizations ADD COLUMN subscription_start TIMESTAMP NULL;
ALTER TABLE organizations ADD COLUMN subscription_end TIMESTAMP NULL;
ALTER TABLE organizations ADD COLUMN trial_ends_at TIMESTAMP NULL;
ALTER TABLE organizations ADD COLUMN add_ons JSONB DEFAULT '[]';
```

